{'default_sort': 4.172418134679167, 'product_name': 'G2 Marketing Solutions', 'is_public': True, 'slug': 'g2-marketing-solutions-review-692878', 'percent_complete': 1.0, 'star_rating': 4.0, 'title': 'G2 Crowd is Awesome', 'comment_answers': {'love': {'text': 'What do you like best about the product?', 'value': "I love the awareness G2 Crowd offers for our product. If someone is simply searching on Google for a CRM system, G2 Crowd pops up and offers all these products with REAL customer reviews. I think that is extremely valuable to both shoppers and companies. G2 Crowd gets hundreds to thousands of people scrolling through their site daily, which offers a great amount of awareness to our product.

One other thing I HAVE to praise is the G2 Crowd staff. Bliss Billingsley was incredibly helpful throughout our training/implementation phase and was always quick to email or call when I had questions. Just last week she transitioned us along to Ashley McDermott, our Relationship Manager. While I'm sad to no longer work with Bliss, I'm equally as excited to work with Ashley and improve our ranking even more!"}, 'hate': {'text': 'What do you dislike about the product?', 'value': "The only complaint I have is that they sent the review emails to our customers back to back. G2 Crowd sends 3 emails to notify your customers to leave reviews and earn gift cards, but I was really hoping we'd be offered the chance to choose the dates of these emails. They sent all 3 emails back to back over a 3 day period, which in my opinion wasn't enough space between emails. Maybe just give customers the option in the future of when to send the emails.
*Disclaimer: I may have had the option to choose and just forgot/didn't realize it..."}, 'recommendations': {'text': 'Recommendations to others considering the product:', 'value': "If you're looking to drive awareness for your product, work with G2 Crowd!"}, 'benefits': {'text': 'What problems is the product solving and how is that benefiting you?', 'value': "We are a very small company and while we are known in our vertical market that we specialize in, we are NOT known anywhere else. Our goal is to drive awareness to our company and product, which then we hope will drive sales. Since we've started this campaign with G2 Crowd, our product has moved from Page 5 to the bottom of Page 3. Page 1, here we come!"}}, 'secondary_answers': {'meets_requirements': {'text': 'Meets Requirements', 'value': 6.0}, 'ease_of_use': {'text': 'Ease of Use', 'value': 7.0}, 'quality_of_support': {'text': 'Quality of Support', 'value': 7.0}}, 'verified_current_user': True, 'is_business_partner': True, 'review_source': 'Invitation from a seller or affiliate. This reviewer was offered a nominal incentive as thanks for completing this review.', 'votes_up': 0, 'votes_down': 0, 'votes_total': 0, 'user_id': '28208566-d9b7-4b8d-9feb-e0f28764ddb8', 'user_name': 'Cassandra Evans', 'user_image_url': None, 'country_name': 'United States', 'regions': ['Americas', 'North America'], 'submitted_at': '2018-05-04T08:30:07.990-05:00', 'updated_at': '2018-05-04T08:30:08.104-05:00', 'moderated_at': '2018-05-05T08:26:25.331-05:00', 'product_id': 'a7d324a4-06eb-4be2-ad8e-65938bce5fd5', 'reference_user_consent': 'unanswered', 'status': 'approved'}

{'default_sort': 4.239359903960307, 'product_name': 'G2 Marketing Solutions', 'is_public': True, 'slug': 'g2-marketing-solutions-review-739332', 'percent_complete': 1.0, 'star_rating': 5.0, 'title': 'Effective. Easy. Fast.', 'comment_answers': {'love': {'text': 'What do you like best about the product?', 'value': 'Not unlike setting up a new profile for a personal account, e.g. LinkedIn or Facebook, standing up a profile for your company is easy. There's a short checklist of items to "complete" your profile, et voila - you are done! 

