There are a few competitors in this space. They are not mutually exclusive depending on your budget needs.  Understand your business pains and objectives clearly before deciding where to start. "}, 'benefits': {'text': 'What problems is the product solving and how is that benefiting you?', 'value': 'We are the stand out leader in our space, with more (happy!) customers than anyone in our space. This is validated by third party analysts, e.g. Gartner, but the voice of our customers was not captured at scale. The primary goal was to have our customers share their experience with our software. However, a secondary benefit is our ability to directly share feedback with out Product Management team. Not happy about a feature or want to do something else with our product(s)? Now our customers have another avenue to share this information.'}}, 'secondary_answers': {'meets_requirements': {'text': 'Meets Requirements', 'value': 7.0}, 'ease_of_use': {'text': 'Ease of Use', 'value': 7.0}, 'quality_of_support': {'text': 'Quality of Support', 'value': 7.0}, 'ease_of_setup': {'text': 'Ease of Setup', 'value': 7.0}, 'ease_of_admin': {'text': 'Ease of Admin', 'value': 7.0}, 'ease_of_doing_business_with': {'text': 'Has the product been a good partner in doing business?', 'value': 7.0}}, 'verified_current_user': True, 'is_business_partner': True, 'review_source': 'Invitation from a seller or affiliate. This reviewer was offered a nominal incentive as thanks for completing this review.', 'votes_up': 0, 'votes_down': 0, 'votes_total': 0, 'user_id': '64d19f96-a8cd-48c9-baf1-37a2f9b032db', 'user_name': 'Zach Deming', 'user_image_url': 'https://media-exp1.licdn.com/dms/image/C5603AQFe0WnqUUv7_Q/profile-displayphoto-shrink_100_100/0/1621635153424?e=1654732800&v=beta&t=v_dYmEuFIsU32isdSVL7TDIcKpBtiO5YMt-5HUZcjx4', 'country_name': 'United States', 'regions': ['Americas', 'North America'], 'submitted_at': '2018-06-14T02:30:05.295-05:00', 'updated_at': '2018-06-14T02:30:05.352-05:00', 'moderate