{'default_sort': 4.376610630836591, 'product_name': 'G2 Marketing Solutions', 'is_public': True, 'slug': 'g2-marketing-solutions-review-1210139', 'percent_complete': 0.85, 'star_rating': 5.0, 'title': 'No One Collects More Trustworthy Reviews Than G2 Crowd! Easy to Implement and Use!', 'comment_answers': {'love': {'text': 'What do you like best about the product?', 'value': 'We really enjoy the G2 Crowd Grid that displays ClockShark alongside other similar time tracking software. Not only is it easy to see how our position changes as we collect more reviews, but this Grid can be embedded in marketing pages to provide leads with a real-time grid view. 

We also really love working with the team at G2 Crowd. Danny took extreme care to understand our company needs and expectations, and even sent us a signed "thank-you" note after our first webinar. (Who does this? Uhm...Danny does!) Our implementation specialist Kelly slowly and meticulously explained how to get our listing set-up. She transformed a super daunting job into very easy subtasks, and weekly met with us to review our progress. It was like eating an elephant, one bite at a time...but with less mandible engagement. Ashley, our main point of contact at G2 Crowd, has overseen our entire G2 Crowd journey, and is quick to resolve any concerns we have. Like, greased lightning fast!'}, 'hate': {'text': 'What do you dislike about the product?', 'value': "I have no complaints about the product, staff, or service at G2 Crowd. One observation is that G2 Crowd prizes quality reviews, and there can sometimes be a delay between review date and the day it posts to your account. Don't wig out: It's TOTALLY normal! They will carefully vet all reviews to make sure they are being submitted by actual software users. Fake news, fake reviews, Pokemon -- the team at G2 Crowd catches it all. "}, 'recommendations': {'text': 'Recommendations to others considering the product:', 'value': 'G2 Crowd goes above and beyond to make sure you are fully acquainted with their platform. Be sure to be open and transparent with your business needs so they can make the proper recommendation for you. '}, 'benefits': {'text': 'What problems is the product solving and how is that benefiting you?', 'value': "We've witnessed increased quality in the reviews of our customers. It's also very easy to contact reviewers through the G2 Crowd portal if you want to follow up with them. 

We enjoy a steady flow of new leads who have encountered us on G2 Crowd in their search for a time tracking software. It's easy to track all leads using G2 Crowd's leads portal. "}}, 'secondary_answers': {'meets_requirements': {'text': 'Meets Requirements', 'value': 7.0}, 'ease_of_use': {'text': 'Ease of Use', 'value': 7.0}, 'quality_of_support': {'text': 'Quality of Support', 'value': 7.0}, 'ease_of_setup': {'text': 'Ease of Setup', 'value': 7.0}, 'ease_of_admin': {'text': 'Ease of Admin', 'value': 7.0}, 'ease_of_doing_business_with': {'text': 'Has the product been a good partner in doing business?', 'value': 7.0}}, 'verified_current_user': False, 'is_business_partner': True, 'review_source': 'Invitation from a seller or affiliate. This reviewer was offered a nominal incentive as thanks for completing this review.', 'votes_up': 0, 'votes_down': 0, 'votes_total': 0, 'user_id': 'df1091ad-7298-49cd-8691-0d99514d6094', 'user_name': 'Verified User in Computer Software', 'user_image_url': 'icons/anonymous-avatar-rorange.svg', 'country_name': 'United States', 'regions': ['Americas', 'North America'], 'submitted_at': '2018-11-20T16:33:22.160-06:00', 'updated_at': '2018-11-20T16:54:21.853-06:00', 'moderated_at': '2018-11-20T20:10:03.910-06:00', 'product_id': 'a7d324a4-06eb-4be2-ad8e-65938bce5fd5', 'reference_user_consent': 'accepted', 'status': 'approved'}

{'default_sort': 4.5128748555944185, 'product_name': 'G2 Marketing Solutions', 'is_public': True, 'slug': 'g2-marketing-solutions-review-1239365', 'percent_complete': 0.38461538461538464, 'star_rating': 4.0, 'title': 'Great social proof, great support. ', 'comment_answers': {'love': {'text': 'What do you like best about the product?', 'value': "In addition to helping us differentiate our products from our competitors, G2 Crowd provides authentic, trusted social proof for buyers researching products. If a consumer searches for reviews of our products, G2C is the first thing they see. The badges, Grid and reference pages are great for sales enablement. 

